    • filterForExport

      public static Person filterForExport​(Person original, int yearsToKeep, long endTime)
      Filter the patient's history to only the last __ years but also include relevant history from before that. Exclude any history that occurs after the specified end_time -- typically this is the current time/System.currentTimeMillis().
      Parameters:
      original - The Person to filter.
      yearsToKeep - The last __ years to keep.
      endTime - The time the history ends.
      Returns:
      Modified Person with history expunged.

    • getOutputFolder

      public static java.io.File getOutputFolder​(java.lang.String folderName, Person person)
      Get the folder where the patient record should be stored. See the configuration settings "exporter.subfolders_by_id_substring" and "exporter.baseDirectory".
      Parameters:
      folderName - The base folder to use.
      person - The person being exported.
      Returns:
      Either the base folder provided, or a subdirectory, depending on configuration settings.

    • filename

      public static java.lang.String filename​(Person person, java.lang.String tag, java.lang.String extension)
      Get the filename to used to export the patient record. See the configuration setting "exporter.use_uuid_filenames".
      Parameters:
      person - The person being exported.
      tag - A tag to add to the filename before the extension.
      extension - The file extension to use.
      Returns:
      The filename only (not a path).
